title: Did the Christian Cod finance campaign raise money for Kyle Rittenhouse?
subtitle: Rittenhouse, 17, accused of killing two people in protest against police brutality in Kenosha, Wisconsin, on 25 August 2020.
author: Jessica Lee
vclaim: :: A mass funding campaign at Christian Sind Goo sought donations to help 17-year-old Kyle Rittenhouse accused of killing two people in a protest in Kenosha, Wisconsin.
